parameters: '異形のタコ怪人！ケルベロスオクトパス！！の巻'

Memimi: It's time for the monster fight...! I can't wait to
battle!! Shark Broccoli-sama, who is our next opponent
organization?

Shark Broccoli: Hmm, you seem to be full of fighting spirit,
Orca Duke... This time, we will be fighting a fearsome
monster again. Without a doubt, a formidable foe on par with
Anomalocaris we fought last time...

???: Don't be stupid, Shark Broccoli!! Don't lump me in with
such weaklings!

Memimi: Ah... Anomalocaris!? Impossible... You mean to say a
monster of your caliber has been defeated...?

Cerberus Octopus: Kekeke... I was just wandering around the
underground city, so I took him down as a warm-up exercise!!
Next up, it's your turn~!!

Shark Broccoli: Cerberus Octopus...! The leader of the dark
organization with a vast territory, "Black Tentacle
Carnival"!! And our next opponent in the monster fight...

Memimi: What a greeting you've given us! Even though you
were an enemy until recently, now you're just a lowly member
of our organization. We will surely repay this favor...

Cerberus Octopus: Kekeke, I don't care about that!! What I
want isn't your pathetic organization. It's the convenience
store, the convenience store!!

Shark Broccoli: You were managing several stores within your
territory. So your target is the convenience store managed
by our organization, GizaGiza Mart...

Cerberus Octopus: Kekeke!! Store management is the most
straightforward hustle for making money!! Once I get my
hands on that convenience store, I'll double its sales with
my wicked production!

Memimi: What a foolish guy... GizaGiza Mart is thriving
precisely because it's a convenience store rooted in the
lives of the local community. We have no need for your
production now!

Bunny-chan: GizaGiza Mart is owned by Shark Broccoli-san and
our organization, so it will be included in the monster
fight rules between the four major organizations in the
city! On the day of the fight, please battle each other fair
and square~❤︎

The face-off between the two organizations ended while
maintaining the tense atmosphere until the very end...

Memimi: Well then, today is finally the day of the monster
fight with Cerberus Octopus. Whether we win or lose, the
organization will undergo significant changes... I must get
psyched up!

Memimi: There's plenty of time before the match starts.
Maybe I'll take a little stroll around town...
